snippet.title: The Outer Worlds 2: First Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
The Outer Worlds 2 is the sequel to the award-winning first-person sci-fi RPG from Obsidian Entertainment. Get ready for an action-packed adventure in a new colony with an even newer crew and the newest graphics! Coming in 2025.
